Some call Python's mascot Monty, after a comedy show called Monty Python. Like it, Python is fun, creative and occasionally a bit confusing! It is a programming language, that you can use to create your own games or tools – everything from 3D adventure games to bathroom timers.
If you have tried a Raspberry Pi, then you probably have used it, but it also comes pre-installed on all Apple and Linux computers!

This web browser, lets you surf the internet as safely and securely as possible. They are dedicated to keeping the internet open and free for everybody. It is one of the best known open source tools, used on Android, Apple, Windows and, of course, Linux computers around the world.
They have even sponsored their own baby "firefoxes" to help the endangered species! (A hint: this mascot isn't really a panda either!)
